== Pronunciation ==
IS-TAR-IA

== English words from ιστορία ==
[[history]] History is the only known word to have origins from ιστορία. 

== Noun ==
'''ιστορία''' (plural: no known plural)
#''learning through research'' 
#''narration of what is learned'' 

== Etymology ==
This is of [[ancient Greek]] origin.

